                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-95-off506 t18220522-95-crimeloc508"></join>, and wash for Lees Shaw. On the 2d of May I hung a counterpane on the furze on the heath, and missed it about three o'clock. Greenfield brought it to me before four.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182205220039"></xptr>
            
                  <persName id="t18220522-95-person899">
                  HENRY 
                  TOOLEY
               <interp inst="t18220522-95-person899" type="surname" value="TOOLEY"></interp>
