                     <interp inst="t18220522-95-person899" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at Hampstead. On the 2d of May I saw the prisoner on the Heath, near the Vale of Health pond, laying in a hole. He 
               <persName id="t18220522-95-person900">drew</persName>
             the counterpane off the furze, wrapped it under his arm and ran away. Greenfield ran and took him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220522-95-person901">
                  THOMAS 
                  GREENFIELD
               <interp inst="t18220522-95-person901" type="surname" value="GREENFIELD"></interp>
