                     <interp inst="t18220522-95-person901" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw him going away with the counterpane, I seized him and he dropped it.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was out of work, this laid on the open field; I thought somebody had dropped it.</p>
